  <?dbhtml dir="buttonComponent"?>
  <title>Concrete toolkit button component</title>
  <para>
  	This component includes standard buttons, check boxes and radio buttons.
  </para>
  <para>
  	A <emphasis>button</emphasis> is a "push" button, usually manipulated with a click of the mouse
  	over the button area. 
  </para>
  <para>
  	A <emphasis>check box</emphasis> is commonly used to select or unselect an option (toggle).
  </para>
  <para>
  	A <emphasis>radio button</emphasis> is used to choose one of a list of options.
  </para>
  		
